[2026-03-08T02:59:34Z] [llm] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Aif5YiBfqBgVyd2M8U7u42","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→{\"id\":\"cloche-028\",\"title\":\"Add cloche-base Docker image and simplify default Dockerfile\",\"description\":\"Create docker/cloche-base/Dockerfile: debian:12-slim + git + cloche-agent. Add docker-base Makefile target (tags cloche-base:latest and cloche-base:\\u003cversion\\u003e). Make docker-build depend on docker-base. Simplify the cloche project's .cloche/Dockerfile and the init template to use cloche-base:latest. See docs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-base-docker-design.md.\",\"design\":\"docs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-base-docker-design.md\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"- docker/cloche-base/Dockerfile exists (debian:12-slim, git, cloche-agent; no node/claude-code)\\n- make docker-base builds cloche-base:latest and cloche-base:\\u003cversion\\u003e\\n- make docker-build depends on docker-base\\n- make install builds and starts correctly\\n- .cloche/Dockerfile simplified to FROM cloche-base:latest + add claude-code\\n- cloche init generates Dockerfile using cloche-base:latest; --image flag renamed to --base-image\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:26:28.701191268-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:40.971081943-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:40.971081943-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\"}\n     2→{\"id\":\"cloche-07g\",\"title\":\"Update cloche init with new project scaffolding\",\"description\":\"Update cloche init to create all current project files: config.toml, version, host.cloche, scripts/prepare-prompt.sh. Replace the old gitignore strategy (ignore .cloche/*/ then negate) with the inverse: track everything, explicitly ignore runtime artifacts (.cloche/*-*-*/, .cloche/run-*/, .cloche/attempt_count/). See docs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-init-design.md.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:26:28.640735412-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:45.477722406-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:45.477722406-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-07g\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-2cc\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:26:28.642105034-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-07g\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-dzz\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:26:28.658281745-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-07g\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-9ea\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:26:28.660178435-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-07g\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-mk9\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:42:47.941084805-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-07g\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-jj7\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:42:48.216963812-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n     3→{\"id\":\"cloche-0aa\",\"title\":\"Evolution Classifier stage\",\"description\":\"LLM-based classification of run prompts into bug/feedback/feature/enhancement/chore. See Task 10 in docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":15,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:07:52.699618555-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:34:26.694741926-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:34:26.694741926-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"labels\":[\"evolution\"],\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-0aa\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-9ud\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:09:29.850421963-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n     4→{\"id\":\"cloche-0yn\",\"title\":\"TOML config system\",\"description\":\"Add config package with Load() for .cloche/config. Support [evolution] section with enabled, debounce_seconds, min_confidence, max_prompt_bullets. See Task 8 in docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":15,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:07:35.362293737-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:23:16.797914218-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:23:16.797914218-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"labels\":[\"evolution\"]}\n     5→{\"id\":\"cloche-0z1\",\"title\":\"Wire cloche CLI binary\",\"description\":\"CLI client with run/status/list/stop subcommands over gRPC. See implementation plan Task 16.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":0,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.89421394-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T13:22:06.329718638-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-20T13:22:06.329718638-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-0z1\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-nq9\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.895418456-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n     6→{\"id\":\"cloche-0zu\",\"title\":\"Update generic adapter to use result extraction\",\"description\":\"- type: task\",\"status\":\"tombstone\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:21:14.714017336-08:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:23:00.287387199-08:00\",\"deleted_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:23:00.287387199-08:00\",\"deleted_by\":\"batch delete\",\"delete_reason\":\"batch delete\",\"original_type\":\"task\"}\n     7→{\"id\":\"cloche-1r0\",\"title\":\"Rewrite engine as DAG walker\",\"description\":\"Replace linear engine loop with concurrent DAG walker. Track active steps, pending collects, and completed results. Goroutines and channels. Validate results against declared list. Fanout and collect support. Implementation plan Task 8.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:25:12.32885009-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:50:29.533256069-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:50:29.533258483-08:00\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-1r0\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-nh0\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:25:12.330042036-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-1r0\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-cow\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:25:12.33160231-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n     8→{\"id\":\"cloche-1vi\",\"title\":\"Add project filters to the web dashboard\",\"description\":\"Add project filtering to the web dashboard so runs can be viewed per-project. Display the final directory name from the project path (e.g. 'myproject' from '/home/user/workspace/myproject'). When project names conflict (e.g. foo/bar and baz/bar), show the parent directory to disambiguate (e.g. 'foo/bar' vs 'baz/bar').\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-27T12:35:00.353790595-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T08:02:08.60585394-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-06T08:02:08.60585394-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\"}\n     9→{\"id\":\"cloche-208\",\"title\":\"Chore: update .gitignore to new cloche pattern\",\"description\":\"After cloche-07g merges, update .gitignore in the cloche project to use the new pattern: remove old .cloche/*/ negation rules, add .cloche/*-*-*/ and .cloche/run-*/ and .cloche/attempt_count/ as explicit ignores. Commit the change.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"- .gitignore has .cloche/*-*-*/ (replaces old .cloche/*/)\\n- .gitignore has .cloche/run-*/\\n- .gitignore has .cloche/attempt_count/\\n- Old negation rules (!.cloche/prompts/ etc.) are removed\\n- git status shows no unintended tracked/untracked changes in .cloche/\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:42:26.844683774-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:45.521089356-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:45.521089356-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-208\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-07g\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:42:48.258587099-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n    10→{\"id\":\"cloche-2cc\",\"title\":\"Rename .cloche/config to .cloche/config.toml\",\"description\":\"Rename the per-project settings file from .cloche/config to .cloche/config.toml. No backwards compatibility needed. cloche init creates a default config.toml with all settings documented. See docs/plans/2026-03-06-config-toml-design.md.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:25:19.846711541-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:41.043760414-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:41.043760414-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\"}\n    11→{\"id\":\"cloche-2ju\",\"title\":\"Implement orchestration loop in cloched\",\"description\":\"Event-driven orchestration loop inside cloched. Triggers on: daemon startup, run completion, and new cloche orchestrate CLI command. On trigger: for each project with orchestration enabled, query task tracker, check per-project concurrency limits, claim highest-priority task, generate prompt, dispatch run. Per-project config in .cloche/config.toml. See docs/plans/2026-03-03-next-features-design.md §1.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"Orchestrator triggers on startup, run completion, and manual command. Respects per-project concurrency limits. Dispatches runs for ready tasks.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:42:45.361039309-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-03T12:52:21.892779417-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-03T12:52:21.892779417-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-2ju\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-31r\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:45:38.705184919-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-2ju\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-43y\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:45:38.745875428-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n    12→{\"id\":\"cloche-2nb\",\"title\":\"Update generic adapter to use result extraction\",\"description\":\"Replace resultOrDefault with protocol.ExtractResult. Marker overrides exit code. Exit 0 = success, non-zero = fail as fallback. Update tests. Implementation plan Task 4.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:24:52.027891556-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:39:43.928824823-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:39:43.928828069-08:00\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-2nb\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-8ze\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:24:52.029049218-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n    13→{\"id\":\"cloche-2sg\",\"title\":\"Add post-run log archival with SQLite indexing\",\"description\":\"On run completion, extract all log files from container to .cloche/\\u003crun-id\\u003e/output/. Write index entries to SQLite (run ID, step name, log file path, size, timestamps). Dashboard and CLI query index and serve file contents on demand. Enhance cloche logs \\u003crun-id\\u003e --step \\u003cname\\u003e filtering. See docs/plans/2026-03-03-next-features-design.md §4.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"Logs extracted and archived on completion. SQLite index populated. cloche logs --step filtering works.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:42:19.148963423-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-03T12:52:21.857300137-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-03T12:52:21.857300137-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-2sg\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-v5x\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:45:38.662096666-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n    14→{\"id\":\"cloche-31r\",\"title\":\"Define TaskTracker port and implement Beads adapter\",\"description\":\"Create ports.TaskTracker interface with ListReady, Claim, Complete, Fail methods. Task struct carries ID, title, description, labels, priority. Implement first adapter for Beads. ListReady returns tasks ordered by priority. See docs/plans/2026-03-03-next-features-design.md §1.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"TaskTracker interface defined. Beads adapter works: lists ready tasks by priority, claims/completes/fails tasks.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:42:37.781893815-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-03T11:38:08.233538356-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-03T11:38:08.233538356-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\"}\n    15→{\"id\":\"cloche-38w\",\"title\":\"Bug: Orchestrator does not close beads tasks after successful workflow runs\",\"description\":\"When a workflow run completes successfully, the orchestrator never calls tracker.Complete() to mark the beads task as done. The task stays 'ready' in beads, so subsequent orchestration cycles re-dispatch it indefinitely. This caused duplicate runs and cascading merge conflicts.\\n\\nRoot cause: orchestrator.Run() claims tasks and dispatches runs, but OnRunComplete() only decrements the in-flight counter — it never updates the task's status in the tracker.\\n\\nFix: After a successful workflow run, call pc.Tracker.Complete(ctx, task.ID). After a failed run, call pc.Tracker.Fail(ctx, task.ID). This requires correlating run IDs back to task IDs, which is not currently tracked.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"- Successful workflow runs mark the associated beads task as completed\\n- Failed workflow runs mark the associated beads task appropriately (fail or reopen)\\n- A task is never dispatched more than once concurrently\\n- Run-to-task mapping is tracked (e.g. in the Run struct or a side map)\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":0,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T13:14:59.985826907-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:49:12.847791831-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:49:12.847791831-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\"}\n    16→{\"id\":\"cloche-3hj\",\"title\":\"Audit Logger\",\"description\":\"JSONL append-only log, file snapshots for revert, knowledge base updates. See Task 15 in docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":15,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:07:52.892498677-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:41:50.566081025-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:41:50.566081025-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"labels\":[\"evolution\"],\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-3hj\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-9ud\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:09:29.989064368-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n    17→{\"id\":\"cloche-3ic\",\"title\":\"Implement per-project health calculator (indicator lights)\",\"description\":\"Domain-level health calculator: given last N runs for a project, return health status (green/yellow/red/grey/blue). Window size configurable per-project, default 5. Green = all passed, Yellow = some failed, Red = all failed, Grey = no runs, Blue = all in-progress. See docs/plans/2026-03-03-next-features-design.md §2.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"Health function returns correct status for all edge cases. Window size configurable.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:42:02.687024565-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-03T11:38:08.131593855-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-03T11:38:08.131593855-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\"}\n    18→{\"id\":\"cloche-3it\",\"title\":\"Wire cloche-agent binary\",\"description\":\"First vertical slice: agent parses workflow file, walks graph, executes steps, streams status. See implementation plan Task 10.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":0,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.640304428-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T12:12:10.062003732-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-20T12:12:10.062003732-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-3it\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-u6c\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.642661493-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-3it\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-cit\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.645862723-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-3it\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-ehk\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.648881668-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-3it\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-hu2\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.65184022-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n    19→{\"id\":\"cloche-408\",\"title\":\"Update validation for collects\",\"description\":\"- type: task\",\"status\":\"tombstone\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:21:14.71625162-08:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:23:00.287387199-08:00\",\"deleted_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:23:00.287387199-08:00\",\"deleted_by\":\"batch delete\",\"delete_reason\":\"batch delete\",\"original_type\":\"task\"}\n    20→{\"id\":\"cloche-43y\",\"title\":\"Implement LLM-based prompt generator for orchestrator\",\"description\":\"PromptGenerator takes a Task and project context, calls configured LLM to generate a prompt suitable for the workflow. Uses the project's agent adapter config. Generated prompt is passed as --prompt to workflow run. See docs/plans/2026-03-03-next-features-design.md §1.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"Given a task, produces a well-formed prompt. Uses project's configured LLM. Prompt is suitable for cloche run --prompt.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:42:41.321151223-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-03T11:38:08.275863287-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-03T11:38:08.275863287-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\"}\n    21→{\"id\":\"cloche-44q\",\"title\":\"LLM Client implementation\",\"description\":\"CommandLLMClient that shells out to claude -p for evolution LLM calls. See Task 17 in docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":10,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:07:52.968002091-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:41:50.602697313-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:41:50.602697313-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"labels\":[\"evolution\"],\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-44q\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-9ud\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:09:30.164783645-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n    22→{\"id\":\"cloche-49c\",\"title\":\"SQLite RunStore adapter\",\"description\":\"SQLite implementation of RunStore and CaptureStore. See implementation plan Task 11.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.690759403-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T12:08:18.795444043-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-20T12:08:18.795444043-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"SQLite RunStore + CaptureStore with migrations\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-49c\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-kcf\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.691929875-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n    23→{\"id\":\"cloche-4eh\",\"title\":\"Wire cloched daemon binary\",\"description\":\"Daemon main: gRPC server, SQLite store, Unix socket listener, graceful shutdown. See implementation plan Task 15.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":0,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.852314324-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T13:22:06.36508835-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-20T13:22:06.36508835-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-4eh\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-95g\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.853504403-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-4eh\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-l1z\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.855135445-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n    24→{\"id\":\"cloche-4ie\",\"title\":\"Daemon trigger and debounce\",\"description\":\"Evolution trigger with per-project+workflow debounce, mutex to prevent concurrent passes. Wire into trackRun() in gRPC server. See Task 18 in docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":25,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:07:53.005657166-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-24T11:09:26.969048189-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-24T11:09:26.969048189-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"labels\":[\"evolution\"],\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-4ie\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-y5x\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:09:30.200543366-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-4ie\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-59l\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:09:30.237425411-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-4ie\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-0yn\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:09:30.272518315-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n    25→{\"id\":\"cloche-4qd\",\"title\":\"Replace NextStep with NextSteps\",\"description\":\"- type: task\",\"status\":\"tombstone\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:21:14.712559443-08:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:23:00.287387199-08:00\",\"deleted_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:23:00.287387199-08:00\",\"deleted_by\":\"batch delete\",\"delete_reason\":\"batch delete\",\"original_type\":\"task\"}\n    26→{\"id\":\"cloche-52f\",\"title\":\"Run and Capture domain types\",\"description\":\"Run, StepExecution, RunState types with lifecycle methods. See implementation plan Task 3.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.349277238-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T12:05:00.4109792-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-20T12:05:00.4109792-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Run, StepExecution types with lifecycle methods\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-52f\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-fv2\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.350429185-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n    27→{\"id\":\"cloche-59l\",\"title\":\"Daemon capture storage\",\"description\":\"Update trackRun() to extract and store new fields from status messages. Set ProjectDir on run record. See Task 7 in docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":15,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:07:35.32137865-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:41:50.493099344-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:41:50.493099344-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"labels\":[\"evolution\"],\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-59l\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-d3p\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:09:29.744330962-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-59l\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-myv\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:09:29.78002563-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n    28→{\"id\":\"cloche-5bj\",\"title\":\"Update example workflows\",\"description\":\"Rename pass to success in all example workflows. Update fix step results. Update wiring accordingly. Implementation plan Task 11.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:25:12.45023414-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:54:37.915671326-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:54:37.915674693-08:00\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-5bj\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-2nb\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:25:12.452228195-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-5bj\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-88j\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:25:12.45529421-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n    29→{\"id\":\"cloche-5jq\",\"title\":\"Update Run model for concurrent steps\",\"description\":\"Replace CurrentStep with ActiveSteps []string in domain.Run. Update RecordStepStart/RecordStepComplete. Fix all callers. Implementation plan Task 9.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:25:12.369774283-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:54:37.880612017-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:54:37.880615303-08:00\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-5jq\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-1r0\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:25:12.370864647-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n    30→{\"id\":\"cloche-5yt\",\"title\":\"Update runner and status reporting\",\"description\":\"- type: task\",\"status\":\"tombstone\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:21:14.718466959-08:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:23:00.287387199-08:00\",\"deleted_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:23:00.287387199-08:00\",\"deleted_by\":\"batch delete\",\"delete_reason\":\"batch delete\",\"original_type\":\"task\"}\n    31→{\"id\":\"cloche-6e9\",\"title\":\"Add cloche delete command for container removal\",\"description\":\"Add 'cloche delete \\u003ccontainer-or-run-id\\u003e' CLI command. Accepts Docker container name/ID or run ID. Calls daemon via new DeleteContainer gRPC RPC. Daemon calls docker rm and updates SQLite. Single container at a time. See docs/plans/2026-03-03-next-features-design.md §5.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"cloche delete accepts container ID or run ID. Container is removed. SQLite record updated.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:41:59.761005025-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-03T12:52:21.676887164-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-03T12:52:21.676887164-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-6e9\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-toz\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:45:38.582029929-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n    32→{\"id\":\"cloche-6lt\",\"title\":\"Implement merge agent (LLM-driven merge in git worktree)\",\"description\":\"Merge agent runs on the host in a git worktree. Given a branch name, it: creates a worktree, pulls latest main, merges the feature branch, resolves conflicts via LLM, runs validation if configured, merges to main on success. On success: cleans up worktree and deletes the branch. On failure: marks merge as failed, preserves branch, notifies via dashboard/indicator lights. See docs/plans/2026-03-03-next-features-design.md §1 Merge Queue.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"Merge agent creates worktree, merges branch, resolves conflicts. Success: branch deleted, worktree cleaned. Failure: branch preserved, merge marked failed.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T11:00:40.12111266-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-03T17:08:13.380584248-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-03T17:08:13.380584248-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-6lt\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-req\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T11:01:15.431388653-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n    33→{\"id\":\"cloche-6vs\",\"title\":\"Add container status to dashboard run detail page\",\"description\":\"Run detail page shows whether the container is still available. If so, shows a 'Delete container' button. Project overview shows count of retained containers. See docs/plans/2026-03-03-next-features-design.md §5.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"Run detail shows container availability. Delete button works. Project cards show retained container count.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:42:30.941042115-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-03T12:52:21.748717246-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-03T12:52:21.748717246-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-6vs\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-toz\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:45:38.540717126-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n    34→{\"id\":\"cloche-76q\",\"title\":\"Full integration test pass\",\"description\":\"Run go test and go vet to verify everything works end to end. Fix any remaining issues. Implementation plan Task 12.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:25:12.493851051-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T21:02:28.815866163-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-20T21:02:28.815868458-08:00\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-76q\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-h9t\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:25:12.495079326-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-76q\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-5bj\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:25:12.496694304-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n    35→{\"id\":\"cloche-78b\",\"title\":\"Bug: Orchestrator ignores beads dependency graph — dispatches blocked tasks\",\"description\":\"The orchestrator's ListReady call returned tasks that have unsatisfied blocking dependencies. Tasks like cloche-07g (blocked by cloche-2cc, cloche-9ea, cloche-dzz) and cloche-208 (blocked by cloche-07g) were dispatched even though their blockers were still open.\\n\\nEither the beads tracker's ListReady implementation doesn't check the dependency graph, or the orchestrator is calling the wrong method. This caused tasks to run before their prerequisites were complete, leading to incorrect implementations and merge conflicts.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"- ListReady only returns tasks whose blocking dependencies are all closed/completed\\n- Tasks with open blockers are never dispatched by the orchestrator\\n- Verify with a test: create task A blocking task B, confirm B is not returned by ListReady\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":0,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T13:15:00.028458264-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:49:12.854707838-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:49:12.854707838-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\"}\n    36→{\"id\":\"cloche-88j\",\"title\":\"Update prompt adapter to use result extraction\",\"description\":\"Inject result selection instructions into assembled prompt and use protocol.ExtractResult to parse LLM output. Remove resultOrDefault. Update tests. Implementation plan Task 5.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:24:52.067985163-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:39:43.966435416-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:39:43.966438292-08:00\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-88j\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-8ze\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:24:52.069151601-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n    37→{\"id\":\"cloche-8bi\",\"title\":\"DSL lexer\",\"description\":\"Tokenizer for the Cloche workflow DSL. Token types, Lexer with NextToken(). See implementation plan Task 4.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.389025368-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T12:05:00.44646389-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-20T12:05:00.44646389-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Lexer with all token types, comments, arrows\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-8bi\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-fv2\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.390262837-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n    38→{\"id\":\"cloche-8td\",\"title\":\"Add domain types for Collect\",\"description\":\"- type: task\",\"status\":\"tombstone\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:21:14.711618079-08:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:23:00.287387199-08:00\",\"deleted_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:23:00.287387199-08:00\",\"deleted_by\":\"batch delete\",\"delete_reason\":\"batch delete\",\"original_type\":\"task\"}\n    39→{\"id\":\"cloche-8ze\",\"title\":\"Add result extraction protocol\",\"description\":\"Create internal/protocol/result.go with ExtractResult function that scans output for CLOCHE_RESULT marker. Last marker wins. Returns clean output with markers stripped. Implementation plan Task 3.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:24:24.152958495-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:31:16.342627663-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:31:16.342630989-08:00\"}\n    40→{\"id\":\"cloche-8zs\",\"title\":\"Chore: initialize .cloche/version in cloche project\",\"description\":\"After cloche-9ea merges, create .cloche/version with content '1' in the cloche project repo. Commit and push so the file is tracked. The daemon will then start incrementing it on future evolution cycles.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:42:26.76039592-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:45.390243196-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:45.390243196-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-8zs\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-9ea\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:42:48.08690651-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n    41→{\"id\":\"cloche-95g\",\"title\":\"gRPC server (daemon side)\",\"description\":\"ClocheServer implementing the gRPC service with RunStore backend. See implementation plan Task 13.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.77088948-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T13:05:56.205201841-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-20T13:05:56.205201841-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-95g\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-49c\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.772095809-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-95g\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-nq9\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.77372075-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n    42→{\"id\":\"cloche-9ea\",\"title\":\"Project versioning: increment .cloche/version on evolution changes\",\"description\":\"After the evolution pipeline makes any change to workflow or prompt files, increment the integer in .cloche/version. File starts at 1 (created by cloche init). See docs/plans/2026-03-06-project-versioning-design.md.\",\"design\":\"docs/plans/2026-03-06-project-versioning-design.md\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"- .cloche/version is created with content '1' by cloche init\\n- config.LoadVersion(projectDir) reads and returns the version\\n- evolution/orchestrator.go increments the version when len(result.Changes) \\u003e 0\\n- Version is exposed in /api/projects/{name}/info response\\n- .cloche/version is not gitignored\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:25:03.406211132-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-07T18:50:08.138606886-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-07T18:50:08.138606886-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\"}\n    43→{\"id\":\"cloche-9ud\",\"title\":\"Evolution Collector stage\",\"description\":\"Gather runs since last evolution, knowledge base, current prompts, current workflow. See Task 9 in docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":20,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:07:52.658144322-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:34:26.658653494-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:34:26.658653494-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"labels\":[\"evolution\"],\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-9ud\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-sdc\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:09:29.815486827-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n    44→{\"id\":\"cloche-9zg\",\"title\":\"Add config file for cloched\",\"description\":\"Add a config file for the cloched daemon so settings like HTTP port, HTTP dashboard enabled, default image, etc. can be configured persistently instead of requiring env vars (CLOCHE_HTTP, CLOCHE_ADDR, etc.) every time the daemon starts.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-27T12:37:00.547392353-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-27T13:10:42.798376569-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-27T13:10:42.798376569-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\"}\n    45→{\"id\":\"cloche-a2z\",\"title\":\"Bug: Orchestrator has no deduplication — same task dispatched multiple times\",\"description\":\"When OnRunComplete triggers a new orchestration cycle, the orchestrator can dispatch runs for tasks that already have an in-flight run (from a previous cycle or manual dispatch). There is no check to see if a task is already being worked on.\\n\\nCombined with the bug where tasks aren't closed after completion, this leads to N duplicate runs of the same task, all racing to merge conflicting changes.\\n\\nFix: Track which task IDs have in-flight runs. Before dispatching, check if the task already has an active run. Skip if so.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"- A task with an in-flight run is never dispatched again\\n- The in-flight tracking covers both orchestrator-dispatched and manually-dispatched runs\\n- After a run completes, the task becomes eligible for re-dispatch only if it was re-opened\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":0,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T13:15:00.067702128-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:49:12.850972801-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:49:12.850972801-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\"}\n    46→{\"id\":\"cloche-ajt\",\"title\":\"Parse collect in DSL\",\"description\":\"- type: task\",\"status\":\"tombstone\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:21:14.715518611-08:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:23:00.287387199-08:00\",\"deleted_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:23:00.287387199-08:00\",\"deleted_by\":\"batch delete\",\"delete_reason\":\"batch delete\",\"original_type\":\"task\"}\n    47→{\"id\":\"cloche-aw5\",\"title\":\"Prompt adapter capture mechanism\",\"description\":\"Add CapturedData struct and OnCapture callback to prompt Adapter. Capture assembled prompt and agent stdout. See Task 5 in docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":15,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:07:35.237187446-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:34:26.623518884-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:34:26.623518884-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"labels\":[\"evolution\"],\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-aw5\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-zgh\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:09:29.674583211-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n    48→{\"id\":\"cloche-cit\",\"title\":\"Graph engine\",\"description\":\"Engine that walks a Workflow graph, executes steps via StepExecutor interface, follows results. See implementation plan Task 6.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.472495908-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T12:06:53.613206074-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-20T12:06:53.613206074-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Graph walker with retry, abort, cancellation, max steps\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-cit\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-ucq\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.473694093-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-cit\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-52f\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.475284248-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n    49→{\"id\":\"cloche-cow\",\"title\":\"Update validation for collects\",\"description\":\"Extend Workflow.Validate to check collect conditions reference real steps and declared results, targets exist, and results in collects count as wired. Implementation plan Task 7.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:25:12.284701944-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:43:59.842939886-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:43:59.842942451-08:00\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-cow\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-lgy\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:25:12.28584644-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-cow\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-i6e\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:25:12.28754196-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n    50→{\"id\":\"cloche-ctn\",\"title\":\"Update prompt adapter to use result extraction\",\"description\":\"- type: task\",\"status\":\"tombstone\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:21:14.714756897-08:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:23:00.287387199-08:00\",\"deleted_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:23:00.287387199-08:00\",\"deleted_by\":\"batch delete\",\"delete_reason\":\"batch delete\",\"original_type\":\"task\"}"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01UrbVxAhg4J7XmRgi48FVn7","session_id":"be3855ff-2535-428a-8a0c-d975245212ae","uuid":"a07319be-c856-4cf7-b67d-2ff25ea0a976"}
