uilt release binaries, Homebrew tap, Docker-based usage, and any other practical distribution methods.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-27T12:35:01.057514125-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-07T18:50:08.214109252-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-07T18:50:08.214109252-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\"}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-d3p\",\"title\":\"Wire capture through runner to status protocol\",\"description\":\"Connect prompt adapter OnCapture to StatusWriter in runner. Emit new status messages with prompt/output data. See Task 6 in docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":20,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:07:35.279067432-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:41:50.456338633-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:41:50.456338633-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"labels\":[\"evolution\"],\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-d3p\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-aw5\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:09:29.709590864-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-dzz\",\"title\":\"Add host.cloche and workflow step type for orchestrator\",\"description\":\"Add a host.cloche DSL file that defines an 'orchestrate' workflow running on the host machine. Add a new 'workflow' step type that dispatches a named container workflow run and waits for completion. Refactor the Go orchestrator to execute the host workflow instead of hard-coded logic. See docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:25:19.791216871-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:45.302965767-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:45.302965767-08:00\",\"cl