Feedback(). By the time update-docs runs, implement.log (full Claude stream-json, 50KB+) is in the output dir, blowing past the context limit. The feedback injection is designed for the fix step but fires indiscriminately for all agent steps.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"- update-docs step completes without 'prompt too long' error\\n- fix step still receives validation feedback\\n- Make feedback opt-in: add a step config key (e.g. include_feedback=true) to control whether readFeedback() output is injected into the prompt\\n- Only the fix step should set include_feedback=true in the default workflow template\\n- Default is no feedback injection when the key is absent\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T12:50:31.844072218-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:40.789030545-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:40.789030545-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\"}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-ehk\",\"title\":\"JSON-lines status protocol\",\"description\":\"StatusWriter and ParseStatusStream for agent-daemon communication. See implementation plan Task 7.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.513987653-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T12:05:00.484197544-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-20T12:05:00.484197544-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"StatusWriter and ParseStatusStream with JSON-lines\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-ehk\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-fv2\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.515306806-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-ewt\",\"title\":\"Full integration test pass\",\"description\":\"- type: task\",\"status\":\"tombstone\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:21:14.719958255-08:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:23:00.287387199-08:00\",\"delete