ucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:23:16.836067031-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:23:16.836067031-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"labels\":[\"evolution\"]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-jj7\",\"title\":\"Chore: add host.cloche and scripts/ to cloche project\",\"description\":\"After cloche-dzz merges and is installed, create .cloche/host.cloche and .cloche/scripts/prepare-prompt.sh in the cloche project, matching the default templates from cloche init. Restart cloched so it picks up the new orchestration workflow. Verify that the next orchestration cycle uses the host workflow path.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"- .cloche/host.cloche exists with the default orchestrate workflow\\n- .cloche/scripts/prepare-prompt.sh exists and is executable (0755)\\n- Both files are committed\\n- cloched restarted; next orchestration cycle logs show host workflow execution\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:42:26.803760641-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:45.433838658-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:45.433838658-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-jj7\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-dzz\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:42:48.174588443-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-jkb\",\"title\":\"Add cloche orchestrate CLI command\",\"description\":\"New CLI subcommand: cloche orchestrate. Sends a manual trigger to cloched to check all projects for ready work and dispatch runs. See docs/plans/2026-03-03-next-features-design.md §1.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"cloche orchestrate triggers the orchestration loop. Returns feedback on what was dispatched.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:42:47.655694437-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-03T15:40:57.538361224-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-03T15:40:57.538361224-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-jkb\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-2ju\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:45:38.787031976-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-jow\",\"title\":\"Add real-time log streaming (SSE) to daemon and dashboard\",\"description\":\"Daemon pipes container stdout to web clients via Server-Sent Events for active runs. Run detail page gets live log viewer showing LLM output, script output, and status messages in real-time. Enhance cloche logs with --follow flag for CLI real-time streaming. See docs/plans/2026-03-03-next-features-design.md §4.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"Dashboard run detail shows live streaming logs. cloche logs --follow works. LLM and script output visible in real-time.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:42:15.456434173-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-03T12:52:21.821209295-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-03T12:52:21.821209295-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-jow\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-v5x\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:45:38.621520934-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-kcf\",\"title\":\"Define port interfaces\",\"description\":\"RunStore, CaptureStore, ContainerRuntime, AgentAdapter interfaces. See implementation plan Task 8.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.554107004-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T12:06:53.648388246-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-20T12:06:53.648388246-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"RunStore, CaptureStore, ContainerRuntime, AgentAdapter interfaces\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-kcf\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-ucq\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\