eated_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:09:29.884318161-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-pik\",\"title\":\"Add health API endpoint and cloche health CLI command\",\"description\":\"Extend GET /api/projects to include health field per project. Add cloche health CLI command showing table of all projects with health status and passed/failed counts. See docs/plans/2026-03-03-next-features-design.md §2.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"API returns health data. CLI displays health table.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:42:04.620982239-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-03T12:52:21.713343966-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-03T12:52:21.713343966-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-pik\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-3ic\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:45:38.457553706-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-q6n\",\"title\":\"Update Run model for concurrent steps\",\"description\":\"- type: task\",\"status\":\"tombstone\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:21:14.717730563-08:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:23:00.287387199-08:00\",\"deleted_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:23:00.287387199-08:00\",\"deleted_by\":\"batch delete\",\"delete_reason\":\"batch delete\",\"original_type\":\"task\"}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-r3b\",\"title\":\"Investigate cloche orchestrate 'No ready work found' despite open tasks\",\"description\":\"cloche orchestrate returns 'No ready work found' even though bd list shows 4 open, unblocked P2 tasks. The daemon-side orchestrator state may not be syncing with the beads tracker, or the concurrency setting (overridden to 1) may be causing unexpected behavior. Investigate the daemon-side orchestration registration, gRPC handler flow, and in-memory inFlight tracking.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"bug\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-07T08:55:13.252440805-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-07T08:55:13.252440805-08:00\"}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-req\",\"title\":\"Implement per-project merge queue in orchestrator\",\"description\":\"Add a per-project FIFO merge queue to the orchestrator. When a run completes with 'done' result, enqueue its branch (cloche/\\u003crunID\\u003e) for merging. Each project processes one merge at a time. Different projects can merge in parallel. Queue state persisted in SQLite. See docs/plans/2026-03-03-next-features-design.md §1 Merge Queue.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"Successful runs enqueue for merge. Queue is per-project FIFO. Queue state persists across daemon restarts.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T11:00:36.498019112-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-03T15:40:57.581589902-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-03T15:40:57.581589902-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-req\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-2ju\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T11:01:15.385283535-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-rxi\",\"title\":\"Subdirectory layout, daemon-side extraction, and poll command\",\"description\":\"Move cloche project files into ./cloche/ subdirectory, replace in-container git push with daemon-side extraction via docker cp + git worktrees, and add a poll CLI command. See docs/plans/2026-03-01-subdirectory-layout-and-poll-design.md and docs/plans/2026-03-01-subdirectory-layout-and-poll-impl.md\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"epic\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:51:36.813893794-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-01T17:20:53.846404063-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-01T17:20:53.846406999-08:00\"}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-rxi.1\",\"title\":\"Add BaseSHA field to domain and persistence\",\"description\":\"Add BaseSHA string field to domain.Run struct. Add ALTER TABLE migration for base_sha column in SQLite. Update CreateRun, GetRun, ListRuns, ListRunsSince to persist/read BaseSHA.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":15,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:51:42.907595121-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-01T15:39:47.752780627-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-01T15:39:47.752783963-08:00\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.1\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi\",\"type\":\"parent-child\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:51:42.909407284-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-rxi.10\",\"title\":\"Implement container liveness check in GetStatus handler\",\"description\":\"Add ContainerStatus struct and Inspect method to ContainerRuntime interface. Implement Inspect in Docker adapter using docker inspect. Add stub in local adapter. Update GetStatus handler to call Inspect and populate container_alive/container_dead_since fields.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":15,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:33.769533418-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-01T17:05:27.33395494-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-01T17:05:27.333958747-08:00\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.10\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi\",\"type\":\"parent-child\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:33.770616384-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.10\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi.9\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:33.772400273-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-rxi.11\",\"title\":\"Add poll CLI command\",\"description\":\"Create cmd/cloche/poll.go with cmdPoll function. Polls GetStatus every 2s, prints step started/completed events, prints state changes. Exits 0 on succeeded, 1 on failed/cancelled. Detects container dead \\u003e1 minute via container_dead_since. Register poll command in main.go and update usage string.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":15,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:39.167819494-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-01T17:13:15.955843443-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-01T17:13:15.955845908-08:00\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.11\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi\",\"type\":\"parent-child\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:39.168848277-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.11\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi.10\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:39.170866599-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-rxi.12\",\"title\":\"Update integration smoke test\",\"description\":\"Update test/integration/smoke_test.go to create workflow files under a cloche/ subdirectory in the temp dir. Verify agent still executes correctly from the new layout.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":10,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:44.091717575-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-01T17:17:18.519973447-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-01T17:17:18.519976804-08:00\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.12\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi\",\"type\":\"parent-child\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:44.092846157-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.12\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi.8\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:44.094668669-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.12\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi.6\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:44.096574508-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-rxi.13\",\"title\":\"Final verification - build, test, vet\",\"description\":\"Run go build ./..., go test ./... -count=1, and go vet ./... to verify everything compiles, passes, and has no issues.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":5,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:49.013542724-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-01T17:20:53.810393049-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-01T17:20:53.810397037-08:00\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.13\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi\",\"type\":\"parent-child\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:49.014730638-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.13\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi.11\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:49.016492025-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.13\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi.12\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:49.018193318-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-rxi.2\",\"title\":\"Remove git daemon from Docker adapter\",\"description\":\"Remove gitDaemons map from Runtime struct. Remove git daemon start/retry loop from Start(). Remove cleanup(), FindFreePort(), gitRepoRoot(). Remove cleanup calls from Stop() and Wait(). Remove CLOCHE_GIT_REMOTE env var from container args. Remove unused imports (net, sync, syscall, strconv).\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":15,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:51:49.104722399-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-01T16:45:37.579202959-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-01T16:45:37.579205584-08:00\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.2\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi\",\"type\":\"parent-child\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:51:49.105926232-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.2\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi.1\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:51:49.107487551-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-rxi.3\",\"title\":\"Remove GitRemote from ContainerConfig and agent push logic\",\"description\":\"Remove GitRemote field from ports.ContainerConfig. Remove GitRemote from agent.RunnerConfig. Delete pushResults(), readUserPrompt(), generateCommitMsg() from agent/runner.go. Remove call to pushResults in Run(). Update cloche-agent main.go to stop reading/unsetting CLOCHE_GIT_REMOTE.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":15,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:51:55.343306502-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-01T16:49:18.121097756-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-01T16:49:18.12110004-08:00\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.3\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi\",\"type\":\"parent-child\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:51:55.344371593-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.3\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi.2\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:51:55.346034895-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-rxi.4\",\"title\":\"Update Docker adapter to copy from ./cloche/ subdirectory\",\"description\":\"Change docker cp source in Start() from cfg.ProjectDir/. to cfg.ProjectDir/cloche/. so only the cloche subdirectory is copied into the container at /workspace/.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":5,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:51:59.983983578-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-01T16:54:06.326457899-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-01T16:54:06.326460895-08:00\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.4\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi\",\"type\":\"parent-child\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:51:59.985402217-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.4\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi.3\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:51:59.986955481-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-rxi.5\",\"title\":\"Add daemon-side result extraction with git worktrees\",\"description\":\"Create internal/adapters/docker/extract.go with ExtractResults function. Docker cp container /workspace to temp dir, create git worktree at project/.gitworktrees/cloche/\\u003crun-id\\u003e from baseSHA, copy temp contents into worktree's cloche/ dir, create branch cloche/\\u003crun-id\\u003e, add and commit, clean up worktree.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":20,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:06.467211468-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-01T17:05:27.26126324-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-01T17:05:27.261266557-08:00\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.5\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi\",\"type\":\"parent-child\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:06.468521782-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.5\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi.4\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:06.470785227-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-rxi.6\",\"title\":\"Wire extraction into gRPC server trackRun\",\"description\":\"In launchAndTrack, capture gitHEAD(projectDir) and store as run.BaseSHA. In trackRun, after container exit call docker.ExtractResults to create the result branch. Update prompt path to cloche/.cloche/\\u003crun-id\\u003e/prompt.txt. Update output extraction path to cloche/.cloche/\\u003crun-id\\u003e/output/. Update StreamLogs output paths similarly.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":15,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:12.877035771-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-01T17:13:15.918049366-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-01T17:13:15.918053324-08:00\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.6\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi\",\"type\":\"parent-child\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:12.879083298-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.6\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi.5\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:12.88259494-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-rxi.7\",\"title\":\"Update cloche init for subdirectory layout\",\"description\":\"Rewrite cmdInit to scaffold into ./cloche/ directory. Create cloche/.cloche/prompts/ instead of prompts/. Write Dockerfile and workflow into cloche/. Update workflow template file() paths to .cloche/prompts/. Add addGitignoreEntries helper to append cloche/.cloche/*/ and .gitworktrees/ to host .gitignore.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":15,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:19.110834041-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-01T16:54:06.365771012-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-01T16:54:06.365776312-08:00\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.7\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi\",\"type\":\"parent-child\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:19.112178441-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.7\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi.3\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:19.114094259-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-rxi.8\",\"title\":\"Update cloche run to resolve paths from ./cloche/\",\"description\":\"In cmdRun, change workflow file resolution from cwd/\\u003cworkflow\\u003e.cloche to cwd/cloche/\\u003cworkflow\\u003e.cloche. ProjectDir sent to daemon remains cwd (host project root).\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":5,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:23.91813571-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-01T17:05:27.298839371-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-01T17:05:27.298841886-08:00\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.8\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi\",\"type\":\"parent-child\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:23.919344193-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.8\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi.7\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:23.921033273-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-rxi.9\",\"title\":\"Add container_alive and container_dead_since to proto\",\"description\":\"Add bool container_alive (field 8) and string container_dead_since (field 9) to GetStatusResponse in cloche.proto. Regenerate gRPC code.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":10,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:28.835726418-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-01T16:54:06.402271696-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-01T16:54:06.402274461-08:00\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.9\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi\",\"type\":\"parent-child\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:28.836804384-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.9\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi.1\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:28.838661512-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-s1j\",\"title\":\"Add dedicated /projects/{name} page\",\"description\":\"Create a dedicated project detail page at /projects/{name} with three panels: orchestrator control, project info, and workflow view. See docs/plans/2026-03-06-project-pages-design.md for full design.\",\"design\":\"docs/plans/2026-03-06-project-pages-design.md\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"- /projects/{name} route exists and renders\\n- Project cards on landing page link to /projects/{name}\\n- Orchestrator panel shows enabled/disabled status, in-flight count, concurrency; toggle and override work\\n- Project info panel shows docker image, version, prompt file git history with diff on click\\n- Workflow view renders steps and wires as a DAG; clicking a step opens a drawer with prompt/script content\\n- New API endpoints: GET/POST /api/projects/{name}/orchestrator, GET /api/projects/{name}/info, GET /api/projects/{name}/workflows\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:25:03.347821436-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T18:25:01.972742703-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-06T18:25:01.972742703-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-s1j\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-8zs\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:42:48.130988517-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-sdc\",\"title\":\"EvolutionStore port and SQLite implementation\",\"description\":\"Define EvolutionStore interface (SaveEvolution, GetLastEvolution, ListRunsSince) and implement on SQLite Store. See Task 3 in docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":20,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:07:35.154118688-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:28:13.006092287-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:28:13.006092287-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"labels\":[\"evolution\"],\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-sdc\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-myv\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:09:29.60418848-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-t62\",\"title\":\"Auto-rebuild stale containers on cloche run\",\"description\":\"Validate that the container image is up-to-date before launching a workflow run. If the project Dockerfile or base image has changed since the last build, rebuild automatically so the container runs the correct cloche-agent and dependencies. This check should happen in the daemon when processing a RunWorkflow request.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-27T12:34:59.78809366-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-07T18:50:08.177394704-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-07T18:50:08.177394704-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\"}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-toz\",\"title\":\"Implement container retention policy for failed runs\",\"description\":\"Change container lifecycle so failed runs automatically keep their container for debugging. Successful runs continue to auto-delete. Preserve --keep-container flag for keeping containers regardless of outcome. Track retained containers in SQLite (container ID, run ID, project, creation time, status). See docs/plans/2026-03-03-next-features-design.md §5.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"Failed runs keep container. Successful runs delete container. --keep-container keeps regardless. Retained containers tracked in SQLite.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:41:56.900426871-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-03T11:38:08.318649084-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-03T11:38:08.318649084-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\"}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-u6c\",\"title\":\"DSL parser\",\"description\":\"Parser that converts tokens into domain.Workflow. Handles steps, fields, wiring, container blocks. See implementation plan Task 5.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.428363172-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T12:06:53.577444897-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-20T12:06:53.577444897-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Parser with type inference, container blocks, wiring\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-u6c\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-ucq\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.429550055-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-u6c\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-8bi\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.431125553-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-ucq\",\"title\":\"Workflow domain types\",\"description\":\"Workflow, Step, Result, Wire types with Validate() and NextStep(). See implementation plan Task 2.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.308280098-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T12:05:00.373106033-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-20T12:05:00.373106033-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Workflow, Step, Wire types with Validate and NextStep\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-ucq\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-fv2\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T11:04:18.309484264-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-uhg\",\"title\":\"Bug: Merge agent resolves conflicts incorrectly — blindly picks sides\",\"description\":\"Replace the merge agent's current strategy (merge + LLM conflict resolution) with a rebase-first approach that treats main as truth.\\n\\n**Current behavior:** Creates a worktree at main, runs `git merge` on the feature branch, then uses an LLM to resolve conflicts. The LLM doesn't understand which side is correct, leading to reverted changes, committed runtime artifacts, and corrupted state.\\n\\n**New algorithm:**\\n1. Create worktree at the **feature branch** (not main)\\n2. `git rebase -X ours main` — replays branch commits on top of current main. `-X ours` in rebase context means 'prefer main's state for conflicting hunks', preserving main's changes while applying the branch's non-conflicting work.\\n3. **Rebase succeeds** → `git update-ref refs/heads/main \\u003crebased HEAD\\u003e` (fast-forward)\\n4. **Rebase fails** (even with `-X ours`) → `git rebase --abort`, mark merge entry as failed, log for human review. Preserve the branch for manual investigation.\\n5. Clean up worktree. Delete branch only on success.\\n\\n**What gets removed:**\\n- LLM-based conflict resolution (`resolveConflicts`, `applyResolvedFiles`, `parseFileSections`)\\n- The `LLM` field on `MergeAgent` (no longer needed)\\n- The merge-based approach entirely\\n\\n**What stays:**\\n- Serial queue processing (`ProcessQueue` recursive drain)\\n- Worktree-based isolation\\n- Validation hook (kept but not wired — future use for test-during-merge)\\n- `gitEnv()` helper\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"- Merge uses rebase-first strategy: git rebase -X ours main\\n- On clean rebase: main is fast-forwarded to rebased HEAD, branch deleted\\n- On rebase failure: merge flagged as failed, branch preserved, logged for human review\\n- LLM conflict resolution code removed from merge agent\\n- Serial queue processing preserved (one merge at a time)\\n- Existing merge agent tests updated to reflect new behavior\\n- ProcessQueue still drains the queue after each successful merge\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":0,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T13:15:00.108777794-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:40.750643398-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:40.750643398-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\"}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-v5x\",\"title\":\"Implement unified log stream in cloche-agent\",\"description\":\"Agent captures all output chronologically to .cloche/output/full.log with structured entries: timestamps, type prefixes ([status], [script], [llm]). LLM conversation output and script stdout/stderr interleaved in real-time. Per-step files (.cloche/output/llm-\\u003cstep\\u003e.log, .cloche/output/\\u003cstep\\u003e.log) written additionally for convenience. See docs/plans/2026-03-03-next-features-design.md §4.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"full.log contains interleaved status, script, and LLM output. Per-step files also written. All entries timestamped and typed.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:42:11.390237656-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-03T11:38:08.19061104-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-03T11:38:08.19061104-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\"}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-vrg\",\"title\":\"Evolution integration test\",\"description\":\"End-to-end test with scripted LLM exercising full pipeline. See Task 19 in docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":20,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:07:53.046568618-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-24T11:10:08.029374546-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-24T11:10:08.029374546-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"labels\":[\"evolution\"],\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-vrg\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-4ie\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:09:30.308637633-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-xyy\",\"title\":\"Simplify code agent switching with fallback chains\",\"description\":\"The process of switching between code agents (Claude, Gemini, Codex, etc.) is onerous. Make it easier to configure multiple agents simultaneously and swap which one is active. Support fallback chains so that if one agent errors, the system can automatically try another (e.g. use Claude unless erroring, then fall back to Gemini or Codex).\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-27T12:35:01.721527868-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-07T18:50:08.250818641-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-07T18:50:08.250818641-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\"}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-y5x\",\"title\":\"Evolution Orchestrator\",\"description\":\"Main pipeline wiring: Collector -\\u003e Classifier -\\u003e Reflector -\\u003e branch routing -\\u003e AuditLogger. See Task 16 in docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":25,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:07:52.930451072-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-24T11:03:14.186375127-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-24T11:03:14.186375127-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"labels\":[\"evolution\"],\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-y5x\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-oa5\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:09:30.023409923-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-y5x\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-cu5\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:09:30.057960664-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-y5x\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-jf5\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:09:30.093320331-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-y5x\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-3hj\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:09:30.12926535-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-zar\",\"title\":\"Chore: build cloche-base image locally (make docker-base)\",\"description\":\"After cloche-028 merges and is installed, run 'make docker-base' to build the cloche-base:latest image locally. Verify subsequent cloche runs use the new leaner image. Also rebuild the cloche project image with 'make docker-build'.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:42:26.719409577-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:45.257187659-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:45.257187659-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-zar\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-028\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:42:47.984336822-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-zgh\",\"title\":\"Status protocol extensions for capture\",\"description\":\"Add PromptText, AgentOutput, AttemptNumber fields to StatusMessage. Add StepStartedWithPrompt and StepCompletedWithCapture methods to StatusWriter. See Task 4 in docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":15,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:07:35.196872961-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:28:13.044962845-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:28:13.044962845-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"labels\":[\"evolution\"],\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-zgh\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-e5l\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:09:29.638987781-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n\n{\"id\":\"cloche-r3b\",\"title\":\"Investigate cloche orchestrate 'No ready work found' despite open tasks\",\"description\":\"cloche orchestrate returns 'No ready work found' even though bd list shows 4 open, unblocked P2 tasks. The daemon-side orchestrator state may not be syncing with the beads tracker, or the concurrency setting (overridden to 1) may be causing unexpected behavior. Investigate the daemon-side orchestration registration, gRPC handler flow, and in-memory inFlight tracking.\",\"status\":\"in_progress\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"bug\",\"labels\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-07T08:55:13.252440805-08:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-07T18:53:56.262733106-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}","numLines":66,"startLine":50,"totalLines":115}}}
